title: Booger McFarland, USC QB Kedon Slovis, And Week 14 Preview
description:
Thursday Night Football and that may be all she wrote for the Patriots. (2:20-8:48) Coach K pulled a classic Coach K.(8:49-14:13) Week 14 NFL preview and its time to start savoring these moments. (16:430-43:46) Cant Lose Parlay is looking great this week. Fantasy Fuccbois.(43:53-49:07) Booger McFarland joins the show to talk about the NFL, Coach of the Year, and who should win the MVP. (57:22-1:37:07) USC QB Kedon Slovis joins the show to talk about being the Quarterback at SC, becoming one of our guys that we will protect, and Cali bros.
